title: 6-7am- Back to the Future Day & Science
itunes:title: 6-7am- Back to the Future Day & Science
description: It’s the anniversary Shannon Hoon’s death, It’s Back to the Future Day, 40 years ago John DeLorean was arrested for a cocaine scheme, Kevin Spacey won his civil suit, Corey Feldmen has a new song, the Noah Schnapp has a hazelnut cocoa spread, California might get some rain, some good PG&E news, the James Webb Telescope took a great picture of the “Pillars of Formation,” how to cope with seasonal affective disorder, and Vinnie reads your texts!
